{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_07_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――という感じで、雫ちゃんに誘ってもらった\nアイドルのライブが最高だったの",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いい刺激になったんですね、良かったです",
      "startTime": 6.9823582966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　私ももっともーっと頑張ろうって思えたの\n佐伯遙子、また明日からがんがん行くわよ！",
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いけない。そろそろスーパーに行かないと",
      "startTime": 20.3451750755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "買い出しなら手伝いましょうか？\n俺も今日の仕事はもう終わりなので",
      "startTime": 26.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんな、悪いわよ……と言いたいけど\nせっかくなら厚意に甘えちゃおうかな",
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね、付き合ってもらって",
      "startTime": 38.6833836238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして。……それにしても\n最近よく遙子さんが買い出しに行ってませんか？",
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}